QuestData.Title: What's Behind The Next Door
QuestData.Description:
If we're going to keep exploring these vaults, we're going to need to open more doors! And that means we'll need more keys.
See if you can find more keys around Forbidden Reach. Every door is another opportunity!
QuestData.LogDescription: Enter the vault and open $1oa more doors using Zskera Vault Keys.

Objectives.Objective: Doors opened with Zskera Vault Keys
